HoloVice - HELP

print & play

Simple version

A game with 'isSpaceChessBoardGameRules' toggled on is a game with one hit, one kill (except mean Savrip).
The center - Dejarik - is accessible. Game ends after 50 rounds, the winner is the player with the most pieces.
The starting player is team red.
A player action consists out of a movement phase and/or an atack phase (except for Takonada & Monnok).
It is allowed to pass only in your second action.

Pieces
Scouts [Ghhhk & Houjix] move in an L-movement (horse in chess),
Brutes [Savrip & Strider] move one step in every direction (1 distance move and 1 distance attack).
Moves diagonal like a bishop in chess;
Guardians [Molator & Monnok] (2 distance move and 1 distance attack)
and Predators [Slug & Takonada] (2 distance move and 1 distance attack).
Note: Predators [Slug & Takonada] can choose to move 1 step up or 1 step down (up is the opponent's direction, down is your location).
This shifts the piece to the other tile color.

Team special
Red: Monnok & Takonada can attack or move twice.
Blue: Savrip, the absolute brute, has 3 lives.
